content_text: My favorite character, fictional character is Iron Man, which is played by Robert Downey Junior. Why is my favorite Is my favorite because he's a very technical person. He's very technical person and he knows how to solve a problem very easily and analytically. He is a very good quality. He's a very analytical, is a problem solving. Whenever there's a problem, he never fails, he never get disheartened, he comes come back with a solution with his gadgets and all that. And that's so cool. So I like him very much. And he has also team building capability. Whenever a problem arises, he gathered the team, motivates them and then tackle the problem very easily.
